5
00:02:02,800 --> 00:02:06,000
Prefect Zhang and Magistrate Li are also on their way.

6
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:08,500
What should we do now?

7
00:02:11,600 --> 00:02:15,500
Mis, how about we dry them by fire?

8
00:02:17,300 --> 00:02:18,800
It won't work.

9
00:02:19,600 --> 00:02:24,200
The Cloud Silk and Gauze is made from silks of different textures.

10
00:02:24,200 --> 00:02:26,400
That's why it shows different colors

11
00:02:26,400 --> 00:02:29,200
under the sunshine.

12
00:02:29,200 --> 00:02:32,900
The fire would ruin the gauze.

13
00:02:33,800 --> 00:02:37,100
It's such a pity to lose such fine gauze.

14
00:02:39,600 --> 00:02:41,400
Er Hu.

15
00:02:41,400 --> 00:02:42,200
Boss.

16
00:02:42,200 --> 00:02:44,800
How much of the Cloud Silk and Gauze are left now?

17
00:02:44,800 --> 00:02:47,800
30 bolts all together at most.

18
00:02:47,800 --> 00:02:49,200
30 bolts?

19
00:02:51,000 --> 00:02:52,700
That's far from enough.

20
00:03:24,800 --> 00:03:29,500
[Su Manor]
We can lose some cloth but we cannot break our promise.

21
00:03:29,500 --> 00:03:30,600
Before the opening,

22
00:03:30,600 --> 00:03:32,800
Tan'er has been working in the shop day and night.

23
00:03:32,800 --> 00:03:34,800
You know that.

24
00:03:34,800 --> 00:03:38,400
Yesterday, the Manager Xi and she checked everything carefully.

25
00:03:38,400 --> 00:03:40,600
No one expected the heavy rain.

26
00:03:40,600 --> 00:03:41,400
Yes.

27
00:03:41,400 --> 00:03:44,600
I said that Tan'er is inexperienced.

28
00:03:44,600 --> 00:03:46,400
It's rainy season now.

29
00:03:46,400 --> 00:03:49,000
We should be even more careful.

30
00:03:49,000 --> 00:03:53,600
We never made such mistakes in our shops.

31
00:03:54,600 --> 00:03:56,600
It was my fault.

32
00:03:56,600 --> 00:03:58,200
Please punish me.

33
00:04:01,400 --> 00:04:02,800
Manager Xi, please get up!

34
00:04:02,800 --> 00:04:04,200
What are you doing?

35
00:04:04,200 --> 00:04:05,400
Get up.

36
00:04:05,400 --> 00:04:07,300
Get up, Manager Xi.

37
00:04:09,000 --> 00:04:11,800
Yesterday, we checked the shop together.

38
00:04:11,800 --> 00:04:14,600
We left after everything was in place.

39
00:04:14,600 --> 00:04:16,400
I was also responsible

40
00:04:17,200 --> 00:04:18,900
for this problem.

41
00:04:21,000 --> 00:04:22,800
Please get up.

42
00:04:24,500 --> 00:04:28,500
We have no way but to delay our opening now.

43
00:04:29,190 --> 00:04:30,599
Tan'er thought she was so smart.

44
00:04:30,600 --> 00:04:34,300
Before the opening, she promoted the Cloud Silk and Gauze so much

45
00:04:34,300 --> 00:04:36,600
that both Prefect Zhang and Magistrate Xu asked me

46
00:04:36,600 --> 00:04:38,900
if they could order the gauze in advance.

47
00:04:38,900 --> 00:04:43,200
If I had known it earlier, it would have been better for me to sell it.

48
00:04:43,200 --> 00:04:44,400
Well, it's over now.

49
00:04:44,400 --> 00:04:47,800
If Prefect Zhang and Magistrate Xu were disappointed,

50
00:04:47,800 --> 00:04:52,400
what would happen to the future of our shop?

51
00:04:52,400 --> 00:04:55,300
It is said that the warehouse was drowned in water.

52
00:04:55,300 --> 00:04:56,900
Are they going to open the shop?

53
00:04:56,900 --> 00:04:58,600
Can we buy Cloud Silk and Gauze?

54
00:04:58,600 --> 00:05:00,600
- Yes.
- That's right.

55
00:05:00,600 --> 00:05:02,400
You promoted the Cloud Silk and Gauze everywhere.

56
00:05:02,400 --> 00:05:04,400
You said it is something we've never seen before.

57
00:05:04,400 --> 00:05:06,000
I came here before dawn to get in line.

58
00:05:06,000 --> 00:05:07,800
I have been waiting all along.

59
00:05:07,800 --> 00:05:09,400
They have nothing for us.

60
00:05:09,400 --> 00:05:10,400
Are they playing with us?

61
00:05:10,400 --> 00:05:12,800
Yes, they are!

62
00:05:12,800 --> 00:05:15,800
Boss, you have devoted a lot to the shop.

63
00:05:15,800 --> 00:05:17,500
We all know that.

64
00:05:17,500 --> 00:05:20,400
But now with 30 bolts Cloud Silk and Gauze and our production speed,

65
00:05:20,400 --> 00:05:22,800
