66
00:05:22,800 --> 00:05:24,000
to meet the demands all the customers.

67
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:25,700
Yes, he is right.

68
00:05:25,700 --> 00:05:27,500
We can delay the opening.

69
00:05:28,400 --> 00:05:30,800
What happened?

70
00:05:31,600 --> 00:05:33,600
Eldest Young Master, you should go back.

71
00:05:33,600 --> 00:05:34,400
Go away.

72
00:05:34,400 --> 00:05:36,000
How dare you!

73
00:05:36,000 --> 00:05:37,600
No manners at all.

74
00:05:42,400 --> 00:05:43,300
Younger Sister.

75
00:05:43,300 --> 00:05:45,400
Go back to your work. Come.

76
00:05:45,400 --> 00:05:47,000
The rain just ruined our warehouse.

77
00:05:47,000 --> 00:05:49,000
Now you are here to see the fun.

78
00:05:49,000 --> 00:05:50,900
You are such a know-it-all.

79
00:05:50,900 --> 00:05:53,400
I care about you, Younger Sister.

80
00:05:54,400 --> 00:05:57,000
It doesn't matter if I'm a know-it-all.

81
00:05:57,000 --> 00:05:59,400
Grandfather also knows it.

82
00:05:59,400 --> 00:06:03,200
How are you going to explain it?

83
00:06:03,200 --> 00:06:07,000
Are you going to open? Is it so hard to let us know?

84
00:06:07,000 --> 00:06:09,600
If you keep dawdling like that, I will smash your shop.

85
00:06:09,600 --> 00:06:13,200
Yes. Smash your shop!

86
00:06:14,100 --> 00:06:16,200
Smash it!

87
00:06:16,200 --> 00:06:18,500
Calm down. You can't go in.

88
00:06:18,500 --> 00:06:23,700
Tan'er, if you agree to run the shop together with us,

89
00:06:23,700 --> 00:06:27,800
I promise I will help you deal with it.

90
00:06:27,800 --> 00:06:30,400
You just need to stay at home.

91
00:06:30,400 --> 00:06:34,900
A woman should stay away from business.

92
00:06:34,900 --> 00:06:38,000
You should stay at home and get well.

93
00:06:38,000 --> 00:06:41,200
Why did you come to our shop?

94
00:06:41,200 --> 00:06:42,600
You are just a matrilocal husband.

95
00:06:42,600 --> 00:06:45,200
It's none of your business.

96
00:06:45,200 --> 00:06:47,600
Why? You want to fight with me again?

97
00:06:47,600 --> 00:06:50,000
I was careless last time.

98
00:06:50,000 --> 00:06:53,200
Then, we are careless this time.

99
00:06:54,400 --> 00:06:56,200
I can't understand you.

100
00:06:56,200 --> 00:06:58,100
What happened?

101
00:06:58,100 --> 00:06:59,600
Where is our Cloud Silk and Gauze?

102
00:06:59,600 --> 00:07:00,400
Look.

103
00:07:00,470 --> 00:07:01,869
Customers are waiting outside.

104
00:07:02,000 --> 00:07:06,700
It is so serious that you won't be able to deal with it.

105
00:07:06,700 --> 00:07:09,000
Tan'er, I knew it when you were young.

106
00:07:09,700 --> 00:07:11,200
You are not

107
00:07:12,500 --> 00:07:15,700
born to be a businesswoman.

108
00:07:20,000 --> 00:07:22,000
Please go back, Older Brother.

109
00:07:22,000 --> 00:07:23,400
I will now announce that

110
00:07:23,400 --> 00:07:25,500
we will delay the opening.

111
00:07:29,600 --> 00:07:31,000
Tan'er,

112
00:07:37,900 --> 00:07:39,800
you've been busy the whole night.

113
00:07:39,800 --> 00:07:41,200
Go have a rest.

114
00:07:41,800 --> 00:07:43,800
I will announce it.

115
00:07:56,600 --> 00:07:57,800
Please calm down.

116
00:07:57,800 --> 00:08:00,200
Our Boss will come out and meet you.

117
00:08:00,200 --> 00:08:01,600
You have said that many times.

118
00:08:01,600 --> 00:08:04,500
Can we buy Cloud Silk and Gauze today?

119
00:08:06,000 --> 00:08:09,400
Everybody, sorry to have kept you waiting.

120
00:08:09,400 --> 00:08:14,400
Ladies and gentlemen, Su's Cloth Store now officially opens!

121
00:08:19,600 --> 00:08:22,000
[Su's Cloth Store]

122
00:08:33,600 --> 00:08:35,000
Ning Yi.

123
00:08:35,800 --> 00:08:37,400
Ning Yi, what are you doing?

124
00:08:37,400 --> 00:08:39,500
Who allowed you to open the store?

125
00:08:39,500 --> 00:08:41,800
Manager Xi, don't just stand here.

126
00:08:41,800 --> 00:08:44,400
Take all the dry Cloud Silk and Gauze out.

127
00:08:44,400 --> 00:08:46,600
Young Master, this is not a joke.

128
00:08:46,600 --> 00:08:47,800
Our Boss has devoted a lot to it.

129
00:08:47,800 --> 00:08:48,800
You can't mess it up.

130
00:08:48,800 --> 00:08:50,800
It's none of your business.

131
00:08:50,800 --> 00:08:52,400
Tan'er, let me ask you.

132
00:08:52,400 --> 00:08:56,200
If we can't open the shop today, second uncle will be happy to see it.

133
00:08:56,200 --> 00:08:57,600
Is that what you want to see?

134
00:08:57,600 --> 00:08:58,400
Of course not.

135
00:08:58,400 --> 00:08:59,800
That's right.

136
00:08:59,800 --> 00:09:01,200
I don't have many strengths.

137
00:09:01,200 --> 00:09:03,200
But I always keep my promise.

138
00:09:03,200 --> 00:09:05,800
I will do what I promised you.

139
00:09:05,800 --> 00:09:07,400
I said I would help you to obtain the seal.

140
00:09:07,400 --> 00:09:08,800
Then I will do that.

141
00:09:08,800 --> 00:09:11,300
Today we must open the shop.

142
00:09:11,300 --> 00:09:13,600
Young Master, you haven't run any business before.

143
00:09:13,600 --> 00:09:15,400
How can you promise that?

144
00:09:16,100 --> 00:09:18,500
Do you dare to trust me?

145
00:09:18,500 --> 00:09:19,800
Let's have a bet.

146
00:09:19,800 --> 00:09:24,800
If I win, you'll be the one who has a say before your grandfather.

147
00:09:24,800 --> 00:09:28,200
If I lose, you won't lose anything anyway.

148
00:09:28,200 --> 00:09:30,600
We just won't open it today.

149
00:09:42,650 --> 00:09:45,720
[Prosperous and Successful]

150
00:09:59,500 --> 00:10:02,400
Everyone. Everyone.

151
00:10:03,600 --> 00:10:05,200
We have Cloud Silk and Gauze.

152
00:10:05,200 --> 00:10:07,600
I know what you're doing.

153
00:10:07,600 --> 00:10:09,000
You let people wait outside.

154
00:10:09,000 --> 00:10:10,600
Then you let us in and we still need wait.

155
00:10:10,600 --> 00:10:12,600
I'm afraid you don't have that Cloud Silk and Gauze.

156
00:10:12,600 --> 00:10:13,800
You must be fooling us.

157
00:10:13,800 --> 00:10:15,400
You must be.

158
00:10:15,400 --> 00:10:17,900
Please calm down.

159
00:10:17,900 --> 00:10:19,400
Same words again.

160
00:10:19,400 --> 00:10:20,800
Just show us.

161
00:10:20,800 --> 00:10:23,000
If you don't have it, I will smash your shop.

162
00:10:23,000 --> 00:10:24,400
Smash it!

163
00:10:24,400 --> 00:10:28,600
As I said, we need these old rascals.

164
00:10:28,600 --> 00:10:30,800
When people are old, they can make more trouble

165
00:10:30,800 --> 00:10:33,200
