166
00:10:33,200 --> 00:10:36,100
Look. So experienced!

167
00:10:37,000 --> 00:10:39,400
Please have a look.

168
00:10:39,400 --> 00:10:41,200
Cloud Silk and Gauze.

169
00:10:51,800 --> 00:10:53,300
Miss.

170
00:11:04,200 --> 00:11:05,400
Young Master.

171
00:11:05,400 --> 00:11:08,400
The Cloud Silk and Gauze is really beautiful.

172
00:11:09,600 --> 00:11:11,800
This is just a trick.

173
00:11:11,800 --> 00:11:14,500
This is our new item, Cloud Silk and Gauze.

174
00:11:14,500 --> 00:11:16,600
You already have it in your hands.

175
00:11:16,600 --> 00:11:21,000
Boss Su, introduce it to everyone here.

176
00:11:22,000 --> 00:11:23,600
Really. It has two colors.

177
00:11:23,600 --> 00:11:25,200
It's exquisite craftsmanship.

178
00:11:25,200 --> 00:11:30,200
We make Cloud Silk and Gauze using silks of different textures.

179
00:11:30,200 --> 00:11:33,600
Under sunshine, it will show different colors,

180
00:11:33,600 --> 00:11:36,400
as unpredictable as the changing clouds in the sky.

181
00:11:36,400 --> 00:11:39,200
If it is used to make clothes, it will be as thin as a cicada's wings.

182
00:11:39,200 --> 00:11:41,600
You will be cool in it and smell good in summer.

183
00:11:41,600 --> 00:11:44,600
- How much will a bolt of it cost?
- Yes.

184
00:11:44,600 --> 00:11:46,200
Just 3,000 cash.

185
00:11:46,200 --> 00:11:48,000
- So expensive!
- 3,000 cash?!

186
00:11:48,000 --> 00:11:49,000
So expensive!

187
00:11:49,000 --> 00:11:50,000
You are robbing us.

188
00:11:50,000 --> 00:11:51,800
Take it easy.

189
00:11:51,800 --> 00:11:56,200
The final price isn't up to us, but you.

190
00:11:56,200 --> 00:11:58,400
