191
00:11:58,400 --> 00:12:00,800
Who said free? Who said free?

192
00:12:00,800 --> 00:12:02,600
You are exactly right.

193
00:12:02,600 --> 00:12:05,200
If you participate in the activity,

194
00:12:05,200 --> 00:12:08,000
