195
00:12:08,000 --> 00:12:09,400
Really?

196
00:12:09,400 --> 00:12:12,400
All staff, listen to me!

197
00:12:12,400 --> 00:12:16,000
All of you start doing your job.

198
00:12:16,000 --> 00:12:17,400
Yes.

199
00:12:40,000 --> 00:12:41,200
[Sale]

200
00:12:41,200 --> 00:12:42,600
[Sale]

