Dear customers, sorry to have kept you waiting.

205
00:13:09,000 --> 00:13:12,800
Welcome to our activity.

206
00:13:12,800 --> 00:13:18,200
All those who want Cloud Silk and Gauze can join in the activity.

207
00:13:18,200 --> 00:13:23,600
