213
00:13:36,800 --> 00:13:38,790
If you get "100 cash off"

214
00:13:38,800 --> 00:13:41,030
that Cloud Silk and Gauze worth 3,000 cash.

215
00:13:41,030 --> 00:13:44,700
Then you can buy one-bolt gauze with only 2,900 cash.

216
00:13:44,700 --> 00:13:46,000
On the other hand,

217
00:13:46,000 --> 00:13:50,000
