218
00:13:50,000 --> 00:13:51,790
With one more friend,

219
00:13:51,790 --> 00:13:54,500
you can get one more chance to throw.

220
00:13:54,500 --> 00:13:58,800
The final price would be 3,000 cash minus

221
00:13:58,800 --> 00:14:02,200
