222
00:14:02,200 --> 00:14:03,700
Are you serious?

223
00:14:03,700 --> 00:14:04,800
I have said a lot.

224
00:14:04,800 --> 00:14:06,400
You have listened for a long time.

225
00:14:06,400 --> 00:14:08,100
Who would like to try?

226
00:14:08,100 --> 00:14:09,600
Me!

227
00:14:09,600 --> 00:14:11,700
This Young Lady. You look very kind.

228
00:14:11,700 --> 00:14:13,800
Come and have a try.

229
00:14:13,800 --> 00:14:16,800
I will turn the table and knock the gong.

230
00:14:16,800 --> 00:14:18,200
Then you can throw the scissors.

231
00:14:18,200 --> 00:14:20,400
Well, come on.

232
00:14:22,200 --> 00:14:24,600
Ready. Go!

233
00:14:28,800 --> 00:14:31,000
300 cash off.

234
00:14:31,000 --> 00:14:36,400
Young Lady, you helped your friend to buy at 10% off the regular price.

235
00:14:36,400 --> 00:14:39,000
If you want the Cloud Silk and Gauze from our shop,

236
00:14:39,000 --> 00:14:42,200
