237
00:14:42,200 --> 00:14:43,000
What about me?

238
00:14:43,000 --> 00:14:45,000
You are helping your friend.

239
00:14:45,000 --> 00:14:48,800
If you want it, you can ask your friends for help.

240
00:14:48,800 --> 00:14:52,000
