242
00:14:53,400 --> 00:14:55,400
What a bargain!

243
00:14:55,400 --> 00:14:57,800
We will record your final price.

244
00:14:57,800 --> 00:15:01,000
Give the money to Boss Su.

245
00:15:01,000 --> 00:15:03,400
